title: Open Weekends For Tour-Newly Renovated-Luxury Amenities-Great Location
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
